# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Ashfall Vault .gitignore
# Created: 2026-06-06 (mirrored from sitl_vault)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── API Keys & Secrets ────────────────────────────────────────
# Match both `.env` and any `name.env`. (A stray `ASSEMBLYAI_API_KEY=....env`
# file was previously committed because the bare `.env` rule missed it.)
.env
*.env

# ── Session Recordings (voices of real people) ────────────────
Session_Sources/Recordings/

# ── Copyrighted D&D Source PDFs ───────────────────────────────
DND_Sources/*.pdf

# ── Obsidian Internal Config ──────────────────────────────────
.obsidian/
.smart-env/
.claude/
.trash/

# ── OS / Editor Junk ──────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Node / Build Artifacts ────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# ── Pipeline scratch (watcher review files, status.json, logs) ─
_pipeline/

# ── Auto-fetched DDB party sheets (other players' data) ───────
# This repo is PUBLIC. ddb_party_sync.js pulls full character sheets that
# players shared only "Campaign Only" on D&D Beyond — republishing them here
# would override that choice. Ignore the generated raw JSON + markdown.
# (The manually-exported *.pdf sheets already in that folder are left as-is.)
03-Characters/01 PCs/Party Character Sheets/_raw/
03-Characters/01 PCs/Party Character Sheets/*(DDB).md

# ── Archived Files ────────────────────────────────────────────
xx_Archive_xx/
